                                                            <span class="blue">Alex:</span>
                                                            Ciao sociis natoque penatibus et auctor ...
                                                        </span>

                                                        <span class="msg-time">
                                                            <i class="icon-time"></i>
                                                            <span>a moment ago</span>
                                                        </span>
                                                    </span>
            </a>
        </li>

        <li>
            <a href="#">
                <img src="assets/avatars/avatar3.png" class="msg-photo" alt="Susan's Avatar" />
